H3.text: Which geological perioed falls between the Triassic and the Cretaceous periods. Jurasic

A4.text: The Jurassic ( juurr-ASS-ik) is a geologic period and stratigraphic system that spanned from the end of the Triassic Period 201.4 Ma (million years ago) to the beginning of the Cretaceous Period, 143.1 Ma.
